            <p part="N">Γενναδίου / comitis Sacrarum Largitionum.</p>
            <p xml:lang="en" part="N">(Seal of) Gennadios, count of the Sacred Largesses.</p>
            <p xml:lang="fr" part="N">(Sceau de) Gennadios, comte des Largesses Sacrées.</p>
